${color2}${cpubar}$color
${cpugraph color1 color8}
Core 1: ${freq 1} MHz
${cpu cpu1}% ${color2}${cpubar cpu1}$color
Core 2: ${freq 2} MHz
${cpu cpu2}% ${color2}${cpubar cpu2}$color
Core 3: ${freq 3} MHz
${cpu cpu3}% ${color2}${cpubar cpu3}$color
Core 4: ${freq 4} MHz
${cpu cpu4}% ${color2}${cpubar cpu4}$color

